Package com.kicas.rp.data

Class Region

java.lang.Object
com.kicas.rp.data.FlagContainer
com.kicas.rp.data.Region
public class Region extends FlagContainer
Contains the data pertaining to a region. Regions can have child regions as well. These child regions are, to some extent, managed by the parent region in terms of serialization, deserialization, and deletion. Child regions also have a priority greater than or equal to the parent region. If their priority is equal to the parent region, then they will adopt the flags of the parent region and are updated whenever the parent's flags change.
